ntents of these terms and conditions within the game service or on the connection screen so that members can know. In this case, important contents such as service interruption, subscription withdrawal, refund, contract cancellation/termination, company\'s disclaimer, etc. among the contents of these terms and conditions are clearly indicated in bold letters, colors, symbols, etc., for make it easy to understand to  the member through a separate connection screen.\r\n2.When the company revises the terms and conditions, the date of application, the contents of the revision, the reason for the revision, etc. shall be specified, and at least 7 days before the effective date, the company will notify the members by posting it in the game service or on the connection screen. However, if the changed content is unfavorable to the member or is a significant change, it is notified in the same way as in the main text up to 30 days before the effective date and notified to the member by the method of Article 27 Paragraph 1. In this case, the contents before and after the revision are clearly compared and displayed make it easy to understand for members.\r\n3.If the company revises the terms and conditions, the member\'s consent to the application of the revised terms and conditions is checked after notification of the revised terms and conditions. In the case of the notice or notice in Paragraph 2, the company will also notify or notify that if the member does not express their intention to agree or reject the revised terms, it will be deemed to have been agreed. If the member does not express their intention to refuse by the effective date of this Agreement, it may be deemed that he or she has agreed to the revised terms and conditions. If the member does not agree to the revised terms, the company or the member may terminate the service use contract.\r\n4.The company takes measures so that members can ask and answer questions about the company and the contents of these terms 