operation policy of each game in accordance with Article 19 Paragraph 1.<br style="word-break: break-word;">a.Restriction of some privileges: Restriction of certain privileges such as chatting for a certain period of time<br style="word-break: break-word;">b.. Restriction on character use: Restriction on the use of member characters for a certain period or permanently<br style="word-break: break-word;">c.. Account usage restrictions: Restrict the use of member accounts for a certain period or permanently<br style="word-break: break-word;">d.. Restriction on member use: Restriction of member’s use of game service for a certain period or permanently<br style="word-break: break-word;">2.If the restriction on use in Paragraph 1 is justified, the company will not compensate for any damage suffered by the member due to the restriction of use.<br style="word-break: break-word;">3.The company may suspend the use of the service for the account until the investigation into each of the following reason is completed.<br style="word-break: break-word;">a. When a legitimate report is received that the account has been hacked or stolen<br style="word-break: break-word;">b. If you are suspected of being an illegal program user or an illegal person in the workplace<br style="word-break: break-word;">c. In other cases where provisional measures for service use are necessary for reasons<br style="word-break: break-word;">   equivalent to each subparagraph<br style="word-break: break-word;">4.After the investigation in Paragraph 3 is completed, in the case of a paid game service, the member's usage time is extended by the amount of time suspended or compensated with an equivalent paid service or cash. However, this is not the case if the member falls under each of the subparagraphs of Paragraph 3.<br style="word-break: break-word;"><br style="word-break: break-word;"><font color="#313131" face="Droid Serif, Nanum Gothic"><span style="word-break: break-word; font-size: 13px;">Article 19